    "The nursing students revealed that ChatGPT was \"highly useful\" (𝑥̅ =3.878; σ=0.755) when it comes to helping them understand basic information, answer questions, and find new ideas.",
    "Specifically, the students yielded the highest satisfaction mean on scale items \"Chat GPT can help me find the information I need quickly and easily\" (𝑥̅ =4.22; σ=0.938) and \"ChatGPT is a valuable tool for learning new information\" (𝑥̅ =3.92; σ=0.950).",
    "Level of Learning Satisfaction based on Ease of Use Ease of Use Metric 𝒙 ̅ σ Rating Chat GPT is easy to use.",
    "4.19 0.940 High It is easy to get ChatGPT to do what I want it to do.",
    "3.96 0.952 High I find Chat GPT to be a user-friendly tool."
